Khaii oniki ho. Avava'ini-ra onamokaravini, ni-khai hora ni'aki. Avakadihojai asohiriki-ra avakava'ipahinivini mani ida khai hora ni'aja. Deua binofi'iki ida avakadihojai asohiriki avava'ini-ra namokaravini. Ni-oathi kapapirani a'onira namakhaniki.
